.TH "itimer_get_remtime" 9 "itimer_get_remtime" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
itimer_get_remtime \- get remaining time for the timer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct timespec64" itimer_get_remtime
.BI "(struct hrtimer *timer "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "timer" 12
the timer to read
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the delta between the expiry time and now, which can be
less than zero or 1usec for an pending expired timer
